@startuml state-token-lifecycle

skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam stateAttributeFontSize 10

title Invitation Token - Lifecycle State Diagram

[*] --> Active : Create\n(admin generates token)

Active : Value = unique string
Active : IsUsed = false
Active : ExpiryDate = optional

Active --> Used : Validate & consume\n(single-use: MarkAsUsed)

Active --> Expired : ExpiryDate reached\n(IsValid() returns false)

Used : IsUsed = true
Used : Token cannot be\n  redeemed again

Expired : ExpiryDate < UtcNow
Expired : IsValid() returns false

Used --> [*]
Expired --> [*]

note right of Active
  Token is distributable
  and can be validated.
end note

note right of Used
  Single-use is enforced
  through the IsUsed flag.
end note

@enduml
